        <div class="panel-body">
          <p>  <strong>How do I send test results to an employer?</strong> Log in, go to your dashboard, 
  scroll down to 'Test Results' section and click 'Forward' on the test result.</p>
  <p>  <strong>How do I view test results?</strong> Go to your dashboard, scroll down and look for 
  'Test Results.' Or, look in the candidates section and click 'Results.'
</p>
      <p>  <strong>How can I tell how long it took for a candidate to take a test?</strong> The candidate's
  test taking time is automatically started when they click the 'Start Test' link, and stopped when they
  submit the test.</p>
      </div>
